#1- I wrote an SQL query that orders products by price.
SELECT item_name, price
FROM superstore
ORDER BY price;

#2- I wrote an SQL query that shows an object's maximum price. 
SELECT MAX (price)
FROM superstore;

#3- I wrote an SQL query that shows the average price of an item in the Kitchen Supplies category.
SELECT avg(price) 
FROM superstore 
WHERE category="Kitchen Supplies";

#4- I wrote an SQL query that shows the average price of an item in the Electronics category.
SELECT avg(price) 
FROM superstore 
WHERE category="Electronics";
